1. *Lek* je lek koji pomaže u vraćanju zdravlja. (A medicine is a medicine that helps to restore health.)

2. *Lek*ari su zaista stručni ljudi. (Doctors are really professionals.)

3. On je veoma dobar *lekar*. (He is a very good doctor.)

4. Ona je školovana *lekarka*. (She is a trained doctor.)

5. To je lekovito *lekovito*. (This is healing medicine.)

6. On je uzimao *lek*ove za svoje bolesti. (He was taking medicines for his diseases.)